--------------
Instructions
--------------

1. Run hadoop first
> ~/hadoop.start.sh

2. Rune hiveserver2 in the background; You need to wait till hiveserver is fully up.
> hiveserver2 &

3. Connect through either:
# hive command
> hive
# beeline command
> $HIVE_HOME/bin/beeline -u "jdbc:hive2://localhost:10000/default" -n your_username